Achievements.Name: Teamwork
Achievements.Description: Watch the credits.

Achievements.Name: Blammo!
Achievements.Description: Earn the Bingo, Bango & Bongo point on a single shot in the Bingo Bango Bongo Traditional game mode.

Achievements.Name: Weather Report
Achievements.Description: Complete an online 18-hole round in the rain using the Live Weather feed.

Achievements.Name: The Comeback Kid
Achievements.Description: Come back from a +5 or worse to finish Even or better, in any Traditional or Online game mode round.

Achievements.Name: Tough at the Top
Achievements.Description: Compete in Play-The-Pros mode and submit your score online.

Achievements.Name: Play with the Big Boys
Achievements.Description: Drive the ball 400 or more yards in the fairway in any Traditional or Online game modes.

Achievements.Name: Maximum Power
Achievements.Description: Complete an 18-Hole round using a max stats costume in any Traditional or Online game modes.

Achievements.Name: Raindancer
Achievements.Description: Play in the rain and score an Eagle or better in any Stroke based Traditional or Online game modes.

Achievements.Name: Riding Spinnaz
Achievements.Description: Sink an approach shot using backspin covering a distance of 5ft or greater in any game mode.

Achievements.Name: Taking Flight
Achievements.Description: Total 50 Birdies with a created golfer.

Achievements.Name: Eye of the Hurricane
Achievements.Description: Shoot under Par through a Gale Force wind in a Traditional or Online game mode 18-hole round.

Achievements.Name: It's All in the Hips
Achievements.Description: Use Precision Putter to sink a 30ft putt without Putt Preview, in a Traditional or Online game mode.

Achievements.Name: Bare Minimum
Achievements.Description: Play a round under Par in a Traditional or Online game mode with a Driver, SW, 5 Iron and Putter.

Achievements.Name: Big Money
Achievements.Description: Win 5 Million Dollars in Live Tournaments.

Achievements.Name: Piece of Cake
Achievements.Description: Post a Top 50 score in a Live Tournament.

Achievements.Name: Migration
Achievements.Description: Total 100 Birdies using a created golfer.

Achievements.Name: Birds of Prey
Achievements.Description: Total 25 Eagles using a created golfer.

Achievements.Name: Big Tuna
Achievements.Description: Play an 18-hole Traditional or Online game mode round in FIR and GIR using only tuned clubs.

Achievements.Name: Aces High
Achievements.Description: Ace a Par 4 or a Par 5 hole in any Traditional or Online game mode.

Achievements.Name: Well-Seasoned
Achievements.Description: Complete a PGA TOUR Season with at least 10 Million Dollars in career earnings.

Achievements.Name: Circle of Life
Achievements.Description: Score an Ace, an Eagle, a Birdie, a Par and a Bogey in a single round of a PGA TOUR Event.

Achievements.Name: Eagle Eye
Achievements.Description: Total 100 Eagles using a created golfer.

Achievements.Name: Ten Thousand Ways
Achievements.Description: Earn 10,000 Player Points in EA SPORTS GamerNet.

Achievements.Name: Challenge the World
Achievements.Description: Complete the Tournament Challenge mode.

Achievements.Name: Sharkies
Achievements.Description: Play 18 holes online against an EA Tiburon team member or against a player who has this Achievement.

Achievements.Name: From Bad to Worse
Achievements.Description: Hit the ball from any bunker into a different hazard, such as a Water Hazard or Out of Bounds.

Achievements.Name: Mulligans Island
Achievements.Description: Use 20 or more Mulligans during an 18-hole round, in any Traditional or Online game modes.

Achievements.Name: No Known Survivors
Achievements.Description: Equip the CEC Mining Hazard Suit

Achievements.Name: Levinator25
Achievements.Description: Complete the first Bonus Challenge in Tournament Challenge.
